    "summary": "The user asks an AI assistant for help writing Instagram captions regarding Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion (DEI) for their coffee shop. After receiving the captions, the user asks for advice on whether to post them, expressing concern that \"old school\" customers might find the topic too political or performative. The assistant advises that ignoring these values is a \"form of inaction\" and suggests a way to frame the message.",
